# clangd merges this with .clang-tidy; ClangTidy Remove overrides enabled checks.
# Catch2: do/while in REQUIRE, short names, assertion literals, __COUNTER__ (Clang 22+).
---
Diagnostics:
  ClangTidy:
    Remove:
      - cppcoreguidelines-avoid-do-while
      - readability-identifier-length
      - readability-magic-numbers
---
If:
  PathMatch:
    - tests/.*\.cpp
    - .*/tests/.*\.cpp
CompileFlags:
  Add:
    - -Wno-c2y-extensions
